We are proud to be a part of the organizational team for Devsigner for a third year in a row. Our little conference grew from a community concept to a destination that gathers amazingly talented speakers, coders, designers, artisans, and tech geeks. Lisa did the branding - she rules! She is the designer behind Drupal Con Portland - stoked to work with her again. Tickets are on sale - get on it to reserve your seat!
